a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BRW\" title=\"Saba Capital Income &amp; Opportunities Fund\">BRW</a>) which traded at around an 8% discount at the time. That discount has narrowed some to 6.96%. This fund has a \u201ctwin\u201d called the </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1887449067/image_1887449067.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742353-saba-a-hidden-gem-with-nearly-10-percent-distribution-yield-and-a-generous-discount", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 18:50:40"}]}